text: Nello Fabbri was a racing cyclist froom Italy. He was born on 15 March 1934 and died on 30 January 2020. Fabbri rode in the 1959 and 1960 Tour de France. == References == == Other websites == Category:1934 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Italian cyclists Category:Sportspeople from Rome
title: Nello Fabbri
